:

1. *Gledaj* da ne zakasniš! (Look so that you don't get late!)
2. Ona je stalno *gledala* prema prozoru. (She was constantly looking towards the window.)
3. *Gledali* smo ga dugo sati. (We watched him for long hours.)
4. *Gleda*š kako se sunce spušta. (You are watching how the sun is setting.)
5. *Gledajući* u njegove oči, shvatila je da laže. (Looking into his eyes, she realized he was lying.)